episodes.title: Mission Admission
episodes.plot: The Mishra family has grown in age, experience and comfort. Aman, the younger son, is now in plus two with big dreams while the elder son has his own desires. But when dreams and desires cross paths, Annu realizes that for his familial duties and responsibilities, some aspirations must wait.

episodes.title: LTA
episodes.plot: Just like every middle-class family, Santosh Mishra travels back home and aspires to use the LTA.

episodes.title: Agua
episodes.plot: Young Santosh Mishra had great expertise in fixing marriages. Santosh Mishra, an ex-Agua is compelled to arrange a marriage that involves a young girl and her mother.

episodes.title: Satyanarayan Varta Katha
episodes.plot: The world where not everything goes according to plan. Be it education, promotion, or expectations. A family plagued with fears of failure takes steps.

episodes.title: Izzat Ki Chamkaar
episodes.plot: Mishra Parivar is hit by health scare. It tries to come to terms with norms in the society we live in. Some members have deep realizations, some change their previously held notions, some grow up.
